=== Subsidiary shrines ===
The current shrine building was moved in from {{ill|lt=Kozu-gu|Q11671792|qid=Q11671792|1=Kōzu-gū}} in the Edo period. Precinct shrines include:

* Idaya Wakamiya (Wakamiya Shrine) - deities: {{ill|lt=Emperor Hanzei|Q329769|qid=Q329769|1=Emperor Hanzei}}, Iwawakino-Mikoto, Otome-no-Mikoto.
* Nanki Shrine - deity: Senior First Rank Tachibana no Ason {{ill|lt=Kusunoki Masashige|Q382234|qid=Q382234|1=Kusunoki Masashige}}.
* Tenmangu
* Amateru Kotai Shrine
* Mitsukuni Inari Shrine
* Mitsuyoshi Inari Shrine

